European Stock-Index Futures Advance; Stoxx 600 Might Extend Weekly Rally

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-07-01T06:04:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/european-stock-index-futures-advance-stoxx-600-might-extend-weekly-rally.html
European stock-index futures gained,
indicating the Stoxx Europe 600 Index will extend the biggest
weekly rally since September.  Futures on the Euro Stoxx 50 Index expiring in September
rose 0.2 percent to 2,854 at 7:03 a.m. in London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
